sion must be similar in all observed\nstars, that is, extreme magnetic activity of the stellar corona that triggers\ngyrosynchrotron emission from non-thermal, accelerated electrons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 26 Mar 2017 22:24:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-28"}
