pturing how these patterns varied across trial\nepochs and trial types.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Mar 2017 03:54:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Nov 2017 22:12:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-04"}
