, where our approach is preferred to the state of the art in sketch\nsimplification 92.3% of the time and obtains 1.2 more points on a scale of 1 to\n5.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Mar 2017 08:23:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-28"}
